{"id":100305,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/苹果获得两项关键界面操作专利，android，bada，maemo-情何以/","date":"2010-08-24T03:59:06Z","modified":"2010-08-24T06:07:12Z","title":"苹果获得两项关键界面操作专利，Android，Bada，Maemo 情何以堪！","content":"<p><p>来自: <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/81467/2\">iFanr 爱范儿 ♂专注于拇指设备的小众讨论 &#8211; FeedzShare</a>  <br />\n<br />发布时间:2010年08月23日,  已有 5 人推荐 </p>\n<hr>\n<div>\n<p><em>Follow <a href=\"http://twitter.com/lordhong\">@lordhong</a>，转载请注明 ifanr.com 及原文链接</em></p>\n<p>2007 年发布的 iPhone 带给我们太多的惊喜，尤其是革命性的移动操作界面和用户体验，获得用户和媒体的一致好评。当时也迫使 1.1 的 Android 系统由黑莓模式的界面转型为 1.5 的以图标为主的触摸界面。其中著名的：</p>\n<p>slide to unlock （划动解锁）：</p>\n<p><img title=\"iSlide\" src=\"http://www.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/iSlide.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"183\" height=\"275\" /></p>\n<p>和虚拟键盘点击弹出放大字母：</p>\n<p><img title=\"iKey\" src=\"http://www.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/iKey.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"216\" height=\"233\" /></p>\n<p>被广泛的<del>抄袭</del>实现在其他的移动操作系统上。</p>\n<p><span></span>然而好景不长……</p>\n<p>上个星期在美国专利局的网站上低调爆出，苹果获得两项关键的界面操作专利：</p>\n<p>&#8211; 划动手指屏幕解锁：<a href=\"http://patft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO2&#038;Sect2=HITOFF&#038;u=/netahtml/PTO/search-adv.htm&#038;r=1&#038;f=G&#038;l=50&#038;d=PTXT&#038;p=1&#038;p=1&#038;S1=D621849.PN.&#038;OS=pn/D621849&#038;RS=PN/D621849\">D621849</a></p>\n<p>&#8211; 虚拟键盘触摸按键弹出放大字母：<a href=\"http://patft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO2&#038;Sect2=HITOFF&#038;u=/netahtml/PTO/search-adv.htm&#038;r=1&#038;f=G&#038;l=50&#038;d=PTXT&#038;p=1&#038;p=1&#038;S1=D621848.PN.&#038;OS=pn/D621848&#038;RS=PN/D621848\">D621848</a></p>\n<p>Android，HTC，你们该怎么办？</p>\n<p><img title=\"aSlide\" src=\"http://www.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/aSlide.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"259\" height=\"194\" /></p>\n<p><img title=\"aKey\" src=\"http://www.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/aKey-360x640.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"259\" height=\"460\" /></p>\n<p>Bada，你怎么办？</p>\n<p><img title=\"bSlide\" src=\"http://www.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/bSlide.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"400\" /><br />\n<img title=\"keyboard\" src=\"http://www.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/keyboard-360x600.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"400\" /></p>\n<p>Maemo、MeeGo，你们怎么办？</p>\n<p><img title=\"mSlide\" src=\"http://www.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/mSlide.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"290\" height=\"174\" /></p>\n<p>虽然笔者非常反感软件和 UI 界面的专利，他们阻止了太多太多的发展和创新，但在这个对股东负责的商业社会，申请专利的理由来得振振有词。其实前段时间 HTC 也起诉了一个独立开发者开发的类似 Sense UI 界面的 Android Widget，为的就是让自己的付费 Widget 铺路。</p>\n<p>虽然目前苹果还没有起诉其他厂家的举动，但这个定时炸弹随时都会爆……</p>\n<hr>\n<p><small>© lordhong for <a href=\"http://www.ifanr.com\">爱范儿: 拇指资讯小众讨论</a>, 2010. |<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/16689\">Permalink</a> |<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/16689#comments\">19 comments</a> |<br />\nAdd to<br />\n<a href=\"http://del.icio.us/post?url=http://www.ifanr.com/16689&#038;title=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E8%8E%B7%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%A4%E9%A1%B9%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%8CAndroid%EF%BC%8CBada%EF%BC%8CMaemo%20%E6%83%85%E4%BD%95%E4%BB%A5%E5%A0%AA%EF%BC%81\">del.icio.us</a><br />\n<br />\nPost tags: <a href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/tag/apple-iphone-ipad\" rel=\"tag\">Apple &#038; iPhone &#038; iPad</a>, <a href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/tag/bada\" rel=\"tag\">bada</a>, <a href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/tag/google-android\" rel=\"tag\">Google &#038; Android</a>, <a href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/tag/htc\" rel=\"tag\">HTC</a>, <a href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/tag/%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9\" rel=\"tag\">专利</a><br />\n</small></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/1017243/tongji.gif\" /><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/997968/tongji.gif\" /></p>\n<p>“要翻墙，<a href=\"http://idangxingdafa.info\" target=\"_blank\">用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[9203],"tags":[8800]}